==English==
===Etymology===
From {{L.}} sui (of oneself) , from {{L.}} ''suus'' (one’s own) + [[-cide]].

===Noun===
'''suicide'''

# the killing of a person by his or her own hand
# a person who has killed him/herself

====Related terms====
*[[suicidal]]
*[[fratricide]]
*[[herbicide]]
*[[infanticide]]
*[[insecticide]]
*[[pesticide]]
*[[regicide]]

